               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 4ra-7ra)&#xD; II)
                     Maṣḥafa lǝdätu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Genealogy of ʾabuna Takla
                     Haymanot” (fols. 7ra-8va)&#xD; - Genealogy of Takla Hāymānot (fols.
                     7ra-8va)&#xD; III) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols.
                     8va-110ra)&#xD; - Introduction (fols. 8va-13rb)&#xD; - Gadla Takla Hāymānot
                     “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 13rb-110ra)&#xD; IV) Maṣḥafa fǝlsätu la-ʾabuna
                     Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Translation of ʾabuna Takla Haymanot” (fols.
                     110ra-120ra)&#xD; V) Taʾāmra Takla Hāymānot “Miracles of Takla Haymanot”: 19
                     miracles (fols. 120rb-131rb)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
