                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The text of the Vita has some characteristics of the so-called "Ḥayq
                        recension" of Gadla Takla Hāymānot. Cp. Mss. EMML n<locus target="#1834"
                           >1834</locus> (EMML V, 310-14); BN, Éth. 342 (GrébGriaule II, 18-20),
                        Ṭānāsee 162 (SixTana III, 202-06). For a (rough) French translation of the
                        text s. J. DUCHESNE-FOURNET, Mission en Éthiopie, 1<ref type="mss"
                           corresp="ES901190">901-190</ref>3, vol. 1, Paris 1908,<ref type="mss"
                           corresp="ES340431">340-431</ref>.</note>
                  </msItem>
